flowchart LR
    SysTick[SysTick ISR<br/>1 ms tick]
    Main[Main loop<br/>time checks]
    Sleep[__WFI()<br/>sleep until interrupt]
    Scan[Every 2 ms<br/>scan one digit]
    Snapshot[Every 250 ms<br/>read snapshot]
    Report[Every 1000 ms<br/>serial report]
    Display[Display<br/>text buffer]
    ADC[ADC1 + DMA<br/>latest buffer]
    UART[USART2 TX<br/>diagnostic line]

    SysTick --> Main
    Main --> Scan --> Display
    Main --> Snapshot
    Snapshot <--> ADC
    Snapshot --> Display
    Main --> Report
    Report --> ADC
    Report --> UART
    Main --> Sleep
    Sleep --> SysTick
